{"tid":1780923,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jennie 狂炸北半球、極限腿根！網暴動：這才是正確的「國際禮儀」","createTime":"2019-12-12T18:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T08:01:28.000Z","uid":44730,"like":22,"dislike":248,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"610efe5a9877787655ae03abef9d847dff416225","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-1-szYSx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-1-szYSx.jpg&h=4aaae9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n Jennie擁有甜美臉蛋與姣好身材，素來更是以會穿、敢穿聞名。日前她一身包得緊緊搭飛機才被驚呼「難道轉性了」？（10）日出席活動就恢復本性，以一身超低胸平口短洋裝，讓北半球和腿根呼之欲出，超惹火的性感程度讓網友大噴鼻血直呼：這就對了！"},{"pid":"3d2e6d19572d46a42c3f9a4206762f0472eb43a1","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":57,"score":-52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-3-jGvuQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-3-jGvuQ.jpg&h=700f2627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只見她穿著一身白色平口短洋裝、胸前拼接黑色大蝴蝶結，讓渾圓美胸全都露，往下一看裙襬更是短到僅能遮住腿根，性感穿搭差點上下都失守！"},{"pid":"ea307923a2400ee22f37c4c2b5c5b5ff1b079f55","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":32,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-4-eOLzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-4-eOLzb.jpg&h=76bf7b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友見狀紛紛直呼：「也太性感了吧」、「天氣冷就是適合這麼 HOT 的裝扮」、「好想幫忙拉住那件洋裝」，並大為贊賞Jennie這身穿搭才是正確的國際禮儀！"},{"pid":"5dd4176f88f72a55003d69a62b5fc2439e615b15","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":26,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-5-7z8f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-5-7z8f8.jpg&h=137dc25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n素有「人間香奈兒」美稱的 Jennie，日前全身包緊緊的機場時尚才讓人質疑怎麼了，馬上就在出席眼鏡品牌 Gentle Monster 活動時，用超性感扳回一城！"},{"pid":"eaf69e9192b0a38dfaf6393b512a0b9254e3100e","tid":1780923,"uid":198503,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"做雞"},{"pid":"7ec500ff9a1f86f8668c50462f5c4b551460fafc","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-6-hEtis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-6-hEtis.jpg&h=b5a96b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有超逆天身材的 Jennie，很難想像剛出道時的她可是有點嬰兒肥，後來因團體需要大量練舞，甚至不需要特別減肥或忌口，就已經甩肉不少；再加上靠做空中瑜珈或皮拉提斯，加強訓練核心肌群，以及攝取大量蔬果、好的蛋白質，不僅對身體比較沒有負擔，也讓身體線條練得更加完美。"},{"pid":"fca8fda94d09942969f12df635c2907612376de0","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-2-mIk93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-2-mIk93.jpg&h=b3d65855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJennie 出席活動穿得超性感！就算披著西裝外套一樣難掩火辣。"},{"pid":"897c1ef854090575d9937192911463c628eded83","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-7-k2rkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-7-k2rkn.jpg&h=4c7763aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJennie 逆天身材示飲食和運動練出來。"},{"pid":"41f3e2ea5099446a84b221746eb31dfec395cdf5","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/12/10/191210-12210-8-X4vSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F191210-12210-8-X4vSw.jpg&h=6e17115b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n性感中又帶有健康美的Jennie，並不走過於纖細的路線。"},{"pid":"97180afabd7435b47469d3da4e537d9d187ba95a","tid":1780923,"uid":55511,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:37:32.000Z","msg":"好撚正規。。。"},{"pid":"464f2fe27b4b2912172ca3f82a89881f93a483ce","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:39:58.000Z","msg":"blink們點睇 <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LEMfr09.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLEMfr09.gif&h=68991de0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38582a9098b41278f81d6fb7b03edf71b1b46186","tid":1780923,"uid":43061,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"小公主正哦<br />\n腳g妹會唔會開小公主post?😁"},{"pid":"9d8ecfed46ddf9cf16eadd890723ae368556dab1","tid":1780923,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小公主正哦<br />\n腳g妹會唔會開小公主post?😁</blockquote><br />\n嗨蛙蛙 <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LEMfr09.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLEMfr09.gif&h=68991de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔喇我又唔係blink <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LEMfr09.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLEMfr09.gif&h=68991de0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb73f770ab2da07e1652776e07e3ad06a46906f0","tid":1780923,"uid":229436,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:47:32.000Z","msg":"胸在哪屁股又在哪<img src=